snippet.title: Frostfire Planet Release Trailer
snippet.description:
Buy it on Steam https://store.steampowered.com/app/1221880/Frostfire_Planet/

Frostfire Planet is a strategy game where each player builds an army of creatures that are sent out in waves against the enemy, around a small 2D world. Use your spells to change the terrain and help your creatures control key objectives. Be the last one standing in this 3 player free-for-all.

Music:
Wintersong by Alexander Nakarada | https://www.serpentsoundstudios.com
Music promoted by https://www.free-stock-music.com
